data.description: Seller is offering a $3000 flooring allowance! Don't miss your chance to experience this inviting 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch-style gem. A warm welcome awaits, as you discover a semi-open floor plan designed for both togetherness and privacy. The spacious rooms provide flexibility for your lifestyle, accommodating gatherings, quiet moments, and everything in between. Your master suite boasts recent updates in the bathroom, ensuring your personal oasis is as luxurious as it is tranquil. But the charm doesn't stop inside—step outside to your vast, fenced backyard, a perfect canvas for outdoor dreams. Whether it's hosting barbecues, playing with your furry friends or gardening in the sunshine, this backyard is your outdoor haven. Located in the Northwoods Subdivision, you're not only surrounded by convenience but also just moments away from Downtown, parks and all that makes a community truly special. Check out today & discover the comfort, space and endless possibilities it offers.
